name: Negative Cash Balance of the week
query:
SELECT s.fuel_station as "Fuel Station:Link/Fuel Station:150",
  s.opening_balance as "Opening Balance:Currency:100",
  s.cash_in_hand as "Cash in Hand:Currency:100",
  s.name as "Shift:Link/Shift:150"
FROM `tabShift` s
WHERE s.opening_balance < 0 or s.cash_in_hand < 0
report_name: Negative Cash Balance of the week
